          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1582890337012-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 18-20 min, add the<strong> onion petals </strong>to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 5 min or until the onion is starting to soften</p><p>Add the <strong>halved walnuts</strong> for a final 3-4 min or until everything is cooked through and the walnuts are toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch the walnuts like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Meanwhile, wash the<strong> shredded kale</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
